{"tid":506590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸小學女生裸露直播","createTime":"2017-12-22T11:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T09:01:22.000Z","uid":35468,"like":291,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"db021f530b4f9e591dc879cc4cba7cb614bcfbc3","tid":506590,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"只要粉絲多 大陸小學女生為好玩裸露直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7335/2850636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7335%2F2850636&d=dU1EKunJxGMjOSOd%2Bn8Pei7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e8c81ace\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7335/2850636</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸知名直播網站「美拍」，被舉發有小學直播脫衣，裸露，以及出現性暗示動作。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞報導，露體直播的小學生稱，不為錢，就是為好玩，她還為自己的粉絲比同學多而自豪，而她在美拍上的粉絲已有近兩萬。<br />\n<br />\n上海晨報報導，據觀看視頻的民眾表示，一名10歲小學女生，脫衣服，脫褲子、呻吟&hellip;&hellip;直播不雅視頻畫面也掃到，小女生的試卷顯示，就讀福建省惠安縣某小學。<br />\n<br />\n華中師範大學生命科學學院教授彭曉輝認為，小女生自己不知道這種方式其實就是對自己的一種褻瀆。父母也有責任，但最大的責任在APP提供者，不應該任由未成年人註冊直播。<br />\n<br />\n華夏匯鴻律師事務所主計時俊任表示，對於直播的經營單位，相關機關應該進行行政處罰，立即禁止任由未成年人開設直播帳號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/12/01/realtime/4305295.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2Frealtime%2F4305295.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=ebf464e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸知名直播網站被舉發有小學直播脫衣，裸露，以及出現性暗示動作。取自澎湃新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/12/01/realtime/4305296.jpeg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2Frealtime%2F4305296.jpeg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=beae677f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸知名直播網站被舉發有小學直播脫衣，裸露，以及出現性暗示動作。取自澎湃新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/NbxsrOh37LYSA/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FNbxsrOh37LYSA%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c9d342cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pa1.narvii.com/5785/1ac0040d64d70f0ac7783d2f1da8892a123e52fe_hq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpa1.narvii.com%2F5785%2F1ac0040d64d70f0ac7783d2f1da8892a123e52fe_hq.gif&h=0c72697b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03a65317c7437c865a5930f9fcde6b2f36fea513","tid":506590,"uid":53568,"like":176,"dislike":7,"score":169,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"好想噁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁細個都岩"},{"pid":"27b52c0c8534f83ebc66cf6a9f7380f79e9eb2b5","tid":506590,"uid":45368,"like":110,"dislike":10,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"雞性難移"},{"pid":"07c1ded044411b2a4756b4890741ae6e298e654b","tid":506590,"uid":76776,"like":496,"dislike":5,"score":491,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d9f1a7d2cae1b38cfd2b7c09b0a85b5e6a11a92","tid":506590,"uid":99582,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"小美麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9f94ae1bb49fddbbfec075f1de05039584a86a","tid":506590,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b0a826e2eb83b9caa11c3b4a0e142b81946e89","tid":506590,"uid":13421,"like":5,"dislike":52,"score":-47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:26:15.000Z","msg":"無碼圖呢"},{"pid":"86ca74094698046ac358d60bd1b3ad73a19e8411","ti